name: Scott Losse
bio: Scott Losse is a cat owner and stand-up comedian from Seattle, Washington. He has performed at Bumbershoot: Seattle's Music & Arts Festival, The Seattle International Comedy Competition, Sketchfest, and lots of other places you've never heard of. Scott's stand-up is smart, absurd, and at times dark. You would probably like it. Scott has appeared on Seattle's Evening Magazine and is the winner of the 2013 Wenatchee Comedy Festival. His cat's name is Kitty. She's a real asshole.
